    • culminateStage

      public boolean culminateStage(int stageOption, int dateSR, int monthSR, int yearSR, int dateER, int monthER, int yearER, int statusN)
      Culminates a stage with the specified parameters.
      Parameters:
      stageOption - The option number of the stage to culminate.
      dateSR - The start date of the stage in dd format.
      monthSR - The start date of the stage in mm format.
      yearSR - The start date of the stage in yyyy format.
      dateER - The end date of the stage in dd format.
      monthER - The end date of the stage in mm format.
      yearER - The end date of the stage in yyyy format.
      statusN - The status of the stage (1 for "completed", 2 for "not completed").
      Returns:
      A boolean indicating whether the operation was successful or not.

      public void registerCapsule(String id, String description, String type, String colabName, String jobTitle, String lessonLearned)
      register a capsule
      Parameters:
      id - the ID of the capsule
      description - the description of the capsule
      type - The capsule type (1 = Technical, 2 = Management, 3 = Domain, 4 = Experiences).
      colabName - The name of the collaborator who created the capsule.
      jobTitle - The job title of the collaborator who created the capsule.
      lessonLearned - The lesson learned from the capsule.
